{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act16side_level_act16side_04_end","storyGroup":"act16side","storySort":9,"storyDependence":"act16side_level_act16side_04_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"GA-4","storyName":"安魂教堂","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"萨科塔能够感受彼此的情绪，而菲亚梅塔是当年的四人小队中唯一的黎博利。莫斯提马与蕾缪安又是否能明白菲亚梅塔的愤怒？","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act16side/level_act16side_04_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act16side_04","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":7,"next":9,"characters":["塞茜莉亚","罗塞菈","安多恩","艾泽尔","莫斯提马","菲亚梅塔","蕾缪安"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g6_laterano_chapelin","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"$warm_loop","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":8},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"再多和我讲些！","id":9},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":10},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"呀，小心手上的蜡烛，别烫着！","id":11},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":12},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"啊！不能捏坏形状......不然就不好看了。","id":13},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"为了妈妈......我要做得完美一点。","id":14},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","focus":"1","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"好啦，我讲得已经够多的了。无非是无聊的冒险，寻常的生活。至于传说中的卡兹戴尔......","id":16},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"说来惭愧，我们都没有去过。","id":17},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":18},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"萨卡兹的卡兹戴尔......一定就像萨科塔的拉特兰一样吧！是萨卡兹们的家乡......","id":19},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":20},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"每个人都开开心心的，也会有棉花糖车吧？还有点心店......大街上会有好多高高兴兴的萨卡兹，大家互相打招呼！","id":21},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"......也许是吧。","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"终有一天。","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"该说说你了，塞茜莉亚。你的爸爸妈妈是什么样的人？","id":25},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":26},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"......其实，我也不太清楚......","id":27},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"我见到爸爸的次数很少......每次要见爸爸的时候，妈妈就会准备很久，带着我在晚上出门，走很远很远......走到树林里。","id":29},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#11$1","focus":"2","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"我们在森林里见面，爸爸总是穿着厚厚的斗篷，似乎刚从遥远的地方赶过来......","id":31},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#11$1","focus":"2","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"我其实不太记得爸爸的长相，但我记得爸爸的角！漆黑又笔直，在月亮下闪闪发光。","id":33},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#11$1","focus":"2","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"他会牵着我的手在树林的边缘散步，告诉我每一棵树的种类和年龄......城外的晚上好安静，连羽兽的叫声都没有，但我一点也不怕。","id":35},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#11$1","focus":"2","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"爸爸老是紧紧牵着我的手，其实会有一点点疼......但我不想告诉他。","id":37},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"每次见到爸爸，我觉得爸爸比我还要高兴......！好像也有点......紧张？","id":39},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"我走累了，妈妈就会背着我回家。我回头，就会看到爸爸站在高高的树下面，一直看着我们，走了很远很远，他还站在那里......","id":41},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"你的爸爸妈妈都是了不起的人。","id":43},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"我觉得妈妈可厉害了！她什么都会！","id":45},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"对了，你看，这是妈妈的守护铳，艾泽尔哥哥放在我这里了。","id":47},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"妈妈说，爸爸根本打不过她......她都是让着爸爸呢！不过我想爸爸也应该很厉害，嗯！","id":48},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","focus":"1","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"哈哈塞茜莉亚，我说的“了不起”和你说的“厉害”，可能不是同一回事。","id":50},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"是吗？那爸爸妈妈一定又了不起又厉害！","id":52},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":53},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"不过，妈妈从来不和我讲她和爸爸认识的故事，我每次想问，稀里糊涂地就被妈妈绕去说别的了......为什么妈妈不告诉我呢？","id":54},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"......当我们还小的时候啊，更重要的事情还有很多。你喜欢看泡茶吗，我小时候可喜欢看泡茶啦，茶水的颜色一层一层地变化......","id":56},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"......","id":58},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":59},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"......罗塞菈姐姐，你现在绕开话题的样子，和妈妈就很像哦......","id":60},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"......其实我也不是什么都不知道。","id":62},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":63},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"昨天我在城里跑了好多地方，除了你，一个萨卡兹都没见到......萨卡兹，不能来拉特兰，是不是？","id":64},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":65},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"所以爸爸和妈妈也不应该在一起......不对，我是想说，是不是有人不让爸爸妈妈在一起？","id":66},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"不，没有什么不应该在一起......这些一定会改变的。不会很久......总有一天。","id":68},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"相爱没有罪过。","id":69},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":70},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"......是吗。","id":71},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":72},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"我们就是为此来到这里的。","id":73},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"到了那一天，我也可以在拉特兰的大街上随便乱逛了？","id":75},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":76},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"当然。","id":77},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":78},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"再也不用偷偷藏在房间里？那拉特兰每一家糖果店我都可以去一次吗？","id":79},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":80},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"一次哪里够呀，塞茜莉亚喜欢去多少次就去多少次。","id":81},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":82},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"呜......真希望那一天快点来......好想快点长大！","id":83},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","focus":"1","id":84},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"是啊，如果你快快长大，也许......","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"不，塞茜莉亚，我们不用那么着急。我小时候，总觉得等长大了，什么烦恼都可以解决掉。可是，等到真的长大了......","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"长大是一件非常非常非常辛苦的事，塞茜莉亚，对你来说更是这样，你肩负着......不，算了。你还小，别去想这些。","id":87},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"2","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"可每个人都会长大呀？","id":89},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","focus":"1","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"......是啊，我们没有选择。","id":91},{"type":"Dialog","id":92},{"type":"character","id":93},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":94},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":95},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$storyendjp_intro","key":"$storyendjp_loop","volume":"0.4","id":96,"musicid":1},{"type":"Text","text":"一直微笑着的罗塞菈露出了有些落寞的神情。","id":97},{"type":"Text","text":"她看向小教堂的窗外，外面是开满鲜花的墓园，再远处，隐约可见高踞于拉特兰城中心的圣像。","id":98},{"type":"Text","text":"她轻轻哼起了歌。忧伤，又依稀带着希望。","id":99},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":100},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"啊，是这首歌！昨天碰到罗塞菈姐姐的时候......","id":101},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":102},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"妈妈教我这首歌的时候说，歌词她记不清楚了，就用啦啦啦代替了。可是曲调真的好好听......本来的歌词，是讲什么的呢？","id":103},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"这是萨卡兹的歌，歌词讲的是一个英雄，他要出发去做了不起的事情啦，人们就唱歌和他告别，送他启程，愿他平安归来。","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"歌里面唱啊，英雄就要出发啦，沿着通往远方的路，去实现他的梦想......","id":106},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"也许路途遥远，但一定，一定......","id":107},{"type":"Dialog","id":108},{"type":"character","id":109},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":110},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","id":111},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#1$1","name2":"avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":112},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":113},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#6$1","id":114},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"艾泽尔哥哥，修士先生！","id":115},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#8$1","id":116},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"在聊什么呢？","id":117},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","id":118},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"先导，日安——都是些有的没的，萨卡兹以前的故事啦，再说说家常话......","id":119},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"可有意思了......我从来没和人聊过这么多。","id":121},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"艾泽尔哥哥，这是你摘的花吗？","id":122},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"是，我想，也许可以萃取一下，给蜡烛加上香味......","id":124},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#2$1","id":125},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"香气可以指引离去之人的方向。","id":126},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#10$1","id":127},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"太好了，谢谢艾泽尔哥哥！","id":128},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#1$1","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"嗯......艾泽尔哥哥，其实......我其实......有点害怕。","id":130},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","id":131},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"葬礼......和妈妈道别......就是真的最后一次道别了，对吗？","id":132},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#12$1","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"真的再也不能见了？就算过节也不行吗？或者......和爸爸一样，很久见一次......是不是也不行？就算......只是摸摸头也不行......？","id":134},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#9$1","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"就算......就算......","id":136},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_352_1#7$1","id":137},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞茜莉亚","text":"妈妈......还有一个天使和驮兽的故事，没有讲完......","id":138},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":139},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"塞茜莉亚......","id":140},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#1$1","id":141},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"是最后一晚了，塞茜莉亚。","id":142},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_363_1#1$1","id":143},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"罗塞菈","text":"塞茜莉亚，今天晚上，我陪你待在妈妈的房间吧，我们都会陪你。你们不会孤独。","id":144},{"type":"character","name":"avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1","id":145},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"艾泽尔","text":"......萨卡兹为一对萨科塔母女守夜。","id":146},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#2$1","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"烛火虽弱，亦能照亮彼岸。","id":148},{"type":"Dialog","id":149},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":150},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":151},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":152},{"type":"Character","id":153},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g7_laterano_ward","screenadapt":"showall","id":154},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":155},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$dignified_intro","key":"$dignified_loop","volume":"0.4","id":156,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":157},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":158},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$1","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"蕾缪安，我们又来看你了。","id":160},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#9$1","id":161},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"给你带了点甜点。","id":162},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$1","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"从大教堂顺出来的水果挞。","id":164},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$2","id":165},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"欢迎。顺便一提，上面的仙人掌看起来很难吃。","id":166},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#4$1","id":167},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"不愧是你，蕾缪安，眼神真好。","id":168},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$2","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"说起来，你们有这么想我，到了要每天来看我一次的程度？","id":170},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#5$1","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"你要是需要，我们每个小时来看你也可以啊。","id":172},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$2","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"莫斯提马，你在献殷勤吗？至于菲亚梅塔......笑得很勉强哦？","id":174},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#1$2","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"出事了吗？","id":176},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":177},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......安多恩。","id":178},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#8$2","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"......","id":180},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#6$2","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"你遇到他了。","id":182},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"拉特兰混进了萨卡兹，而我在追捕萨卡兹的时候......正面撞上了他的源石技艺。","id":184},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#9$2","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"是吗，没受伤就好。","id":186},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#4$1","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"蕾缪安，你在这里没问题吗？毕竟只是普通医院，万一......","id":188},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#8$2","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"他已经来过了。","id":190},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你说什——","id":192},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#6$1","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......唉。","id":194},{"type":"Dialog","id":195},{"type":"character","id":196},{"type":"Text","text":"病房中一时寂静。","id":197},{"type":"Text","text":"蕾缪安看向桌上的瓶花。","id":198},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......","id":200},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你们说起他的态度，简直就像在谈论周末的野餐。","id":202},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":203},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"蕾缪安，我不想和你生气......","id":204},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":205},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"但唯独在这件事上......无论是你，还是莫斯提马，每一次，每一次，我提起那时的事情，你们就会露出一样的表情......","id":206},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#4$1","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"看到你们的样子，我会觉得......好像那天发疯的人不是他，而是我。","id":208},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#6$1","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......我们只是感受到了。","id":210},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":211},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"又是你们萨科塔那一套？好，你感受到了，那你又为什么向他举铳？","id":212},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#8$1","id":213},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"两回事。不论他当时有多......我也不可能让他夺走锁与匙。","id":214},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":215},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"那之后呢？他害得你堕天了......！你就这样无所谓？","id":216},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":217},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"蕾缪安，他的源石技艺，把你伤成这样，在病床上昏迷了五年......你也无所谓吗？","id":218},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#1$2","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"菲亚梅塔......","id":220},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#1$2","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"相信我，我们是与你一边的。","id":222},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#9$2","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"只是，我确实能感受......","id":224},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1","id":225},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......我不想再听到这个词。","id":226},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":227},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你们是不是觉得，我的生气很多余？","id":228},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#6$2","id":229},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"怎么会呢，菲亚梅塔，我明白......","id":230},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":231},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"对的，当然了，你们都明白。","id":232},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"只有我不明白。","id":234},{"type":"dialog","id":235},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":236},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1.5","id":237},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":238},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#4$1","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"喂，菲亚梅塔！","id":240},{"type":"dialog","id":241},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":242},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":243},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","text":"","id":244},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#6$2","id":245},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"唉......","id":246},{"type":"Dialog","id":247},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":248},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":249},{"type":"Character","id":250},{"type":"Background","image":"26_g11_laterano_alley","screenadapt":"showall","id":251},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":252},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":253},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":254},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","text":"","id":255},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"菲亚梅塔，菲亚梅塔！","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"微光守夜人！","id":257},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":258},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"50","vibrato":"50","randomness":"50","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":259},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"揍你啊！","id":260},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#6$1","id":261},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"你听我说！","id":262},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":263},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"莫斯提马，我告诉你！","id":264},{"type":"dialog","id":265},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":266},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":267},{"type":"Character","id":268},{"type":"Image","image":"26_i05","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","x":"150","y":"-80","id":269},{"type":"ImageTween","xScaleTo":"0.8","yScaleTo":"0.8","duration":"40","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","block":"false","id":270},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_cloakmovement","id":271},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":272},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.51","id":273},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"听好了，我再也受不了你们这些混蛋萨科塔了！什么共感，什么互相理解！我根本就不想懂！","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"光环是把你们这些天使的脑子烧坏了吗？你和蕾缪安，差点死在那片废墟里！","id":275},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你们为什么不生气？你们为什么不愤怒？为什么只有我......我的愤怒格格不入？","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"别再给我摆那种故作高深的笑脸，说起什么都无所谓的态度！你不得不离开拉特兰，到处奔波，风餐露宿，居无定所，是拜谁所赐？！","id":277},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"我一路跟着你到维多利亚，到莱塔尼亚，到萨尔贡，到炎国......","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你以为到底是为了什么？！","id":279},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你，蕾缪安，安多恩......我们的小队。我们有过那么......相互信任的时候。","id":280},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"他有什么了不得的苦衷？他凭什么背叛这些信任？你们凭什么要理解他？我又为什么要理解他！","id":281},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你知道我有多舍不得那段日子......？每一次有惊无险地完成任务......每一次蕾缪安带我们去喝酒......每一次我们去试新开的甜品店......","id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"甚至每一次他帮大家改报告......","id":283},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"他有什么理由，就随手毁了这一切......？！！","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"那样的日子......","id":285},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"那样的日子，我是在乎的啊......","id":286},{"type":"dialog","id":287},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":288},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":289},{"type":"Character","id":290},{"type":"Image","id":291},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":292},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":293},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#6$1","id":294},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......是吗。","id":295},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":296},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......","id":297},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#6$1","id":298},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......","id":299},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#9$1","id":300},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"菲......","id":301},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1","id":302},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"拉特兰的鸢尾花。","id":303},{"type":"dialog","id":304},{"type":"character","id":305},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":306},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":307},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$newhope01_intro","key":"$newhope01_loop","volume":"0.4","id":308,"musicid":3},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#1$1","id":309},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":310},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$1","id":311},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......","id":312},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1","id":313},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"只长在圣马尔索中心花园、夕辉礼拜堂和司提望区安魂教堂这几个地方。","id":314},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$1","id":315},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"嗯。","id":316},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#10$1","id":317},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"走吧，我们一起。","id":318},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$1","id":319},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"......你可是我的监视者，可别让我受伤了哦。","id":320},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1","id":321},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"......","id":322},{"type":"Dialog","id":323},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":324},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":325},{"type":"Dialog","id":326},{"type":"Character","id":327},{"type":"Image","id":328}],"characters":["塞茜莉亚","罗塞菈","安多恩","艾泽尔","莫斯提马","菲亚梅塔","蕾缪安"]}